Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.02,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我并不想拿起利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.11,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.82,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不流泪 不畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}燃烧 燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你告诉我 我错过了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.75,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}仍在浓雾中彷徨
